{"tid":1050451,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[回帶2017！]陸頌雄心急未過路試先買心儀美帝車！！","createTime":"2019-03-07T02:02:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-07T02:36:48.000Z","uid":61280,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"99e029728d0bf6677b260baad97165f02f9729e8","tid":1050451,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T02:02:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/07/100209_42485f164206c83025486b7892eefcad.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F07%2F100209_42485f164206c83025486b7892eefcad.png&h=c32b98b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59f096de1b17c3fb149fc02425fe3083e0a06e2e","tid":1050451,"uid":61280,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T02:03:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/07/100209_42485f164206c83025486b7892eefcad.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F07%2F100209_42485f164206c83025486b7892eefcad.png&h=c32b98b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/936297/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/936297/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"716be56113d394db2c78136a950543f78799d345","tid":1050451,"uid":61280,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T02:05:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q6wmf8o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ6wmf8o.jpg&h=c36fbb6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《流浪地球》呢？？？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>水人話marvel<br />\n跟住話播錯 流浪地球<br />\n再話係中國版嚟<br />\n咪咁搞掂</blockquote><br />\n<blockquote><img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190306/s00001/3153f5a2fa4ce33e0b0366a46077bf85.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190306%2Fs00001%2F3153f5a2fa4ce33e0b0366a46077bf85.jpg&h=8e196d1c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今天是二十四節氣中的驚蟄，傳統上，不少香港人會到鵝頸橋「打小人」求平安順遂。來到21世紀，「打小人」亦進化至「電子世界」，工聯會立法會議員陸頌雄就以美國駐港總領事唐偉康當「人辦」，教人用手機App「打小人」，形容「係具有香港特色嘅風俗智慧」。<br />\n<br />\n陸頌雄下午於facebook上載「打小人」App教學圖片，圖中主角為唐偉康。他表示，需要跟着口訣節奏搖動或拍打手機，如「打你個小人頭，等你有氣冇碇抖」，待相中人臉部扭曲便完成。<br />\n<br />\n陸頌雄解釋，因唐偉康「亂噏」、「衰多口」，故找他做「人辦」，又形容「打小人」可令人心情舒暢。陸頌雄並標籤了美國駐港總領事館。<br />\n<br />\n美國駐港總領事唐偉康日前表示，香港過去數年呈現側重「一國」，令「兩制」未能發揮最大益處的趨勢，而內地對本港施加的壓力，影響香港政治生態及收窄政治空間，更令美方擔憂的是，未來會進一步威脅香港營商環境。<br />\n<br />\n外交部駐港特派員公署之後向美國駐港總領事館提出嚴正交涉，亦有建制派要求唐偉康道歉。唐偉康表明不會道歉，表示自己雖然道出「一國兩制」面對什麼風險，但其評論整體是正面，認為人們應從前文後理理解其說話。<br />\n<br />\n[ul]<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190306/s00001/1551854642515/【emily-online】陸頌雄驚蟄用唐偉康做「人辦」教「打小人」[/url]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190306%2Fs00001%2F1551854642515%2F%E3%80%90emily-online%E3%80%91%E9%99%B8%E9%A0%8C%E9%9B%84%E9%A9%9A%E8%9F%84%E7%94%A8%E5%94%90%E5%81%89%E5%BA%B7%E5%81%9A%E3%80%8C%E4%BA%BA%E8%BE%A6%E3%80%8D%E6%95%99%E3%80%8C%E6%89%93%E5%B0%8F%E4%BA%BA%E3%80%8D%5B%2Furl%5D&d=m7n5JD7ZMd19sx07z0x1QHO0ZW31AiaZ%2BXmqixBX3cM%3D&h=d3c4ef78\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190306%2Fs00001%2F1551854642515%2F%E3%80%90emily-online%E3%80%91%E9%99%B8%E9%A0%8C%E9%9B%84%E9%A9%9A%E8%9F%84%E7%94%A8%E5%94%90%E5%81%89%E5%BA%B7%E5%81%9A%E3%80%8C%E4%BA%BA%E8%BE%A6%E3%80%8D%E6%95%99%E3%80%8C%E6%89%93%E5%B0%8F%E4%BA%BA%E3%80%8D%5B%2Furl%5D&h=b3c12571\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190306/s00001/1551854642515/【emily-online】陸頌雄驚蟄用唐偉康做「人辦」教「打小人」[/url]</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><blockquote>《維也納外交關係公約》第二十九條規定，&ldquo;外交代表人身不得侵犯。外交代表不受任何方式之逮捕或拘禁。<span style=\"color: red;\">接受國對外交代表應特示尊重，並應採取一切適當步驟以防止其人身、自由或尊嚴受有任何侵犯</span>。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fmcoprc.gov.hk/chn/syzx/lbzs/t9041.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.fmcoprc.gov.hk%2Fchn%2Fsyzx%2Flbzs%2Ft9041.htm&d=m7n5JD7ZMd19sx07z0x1QHO0ZW31AiaZ%2BXmqixBX3cM%3D&h=db129f49\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.fmcoprc.gov.hk/chn/syzx/lbzs/t9041.htm</a></blockquote><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我做野放心啦，Quote埋俾侵侵架嗱！！！！</span></span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">睇黎爆醬好撚想做焦土之父！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"fd7a36d721768942d26d0f722e764402801e4bf1","tid":1050451,"uid":61280,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T02:06:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">陳勇請留意：係陸頒雄，咪搵錯人呀！！！！</span></span></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4db3d751f4ac3287a8c2d2406a6270cfce04db9b","tid":1050451,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"